{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act31side", "eventName": "懷黍離", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "HS-5", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "紡綾羅", "storyInfo": "千年前因為一場意外而被埋在土地裡的邪魔碎片，在此時成了威脅整座大荒城安全的元兇。在所有人束手無策的時候，黍獨自走向了農田。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "47_g7_fieldhouse", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像是做夢一樣。"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她走過了很長一段路，在冰天雪地中翻山越嶺，路的盡頭是一片望不到邊際的稻田。"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "豐碩的稻穗像金子一樣，黃燦燦的。不知是誰把它們種在了這裡，不知為何它們能在這裡長得如此繁盛。"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真好啊。"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“就留在這裡吧。”"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她聽到有一個聲音在呼喚她。"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不……不。"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她還記得，自己還有沒做完的事，自己還有要回去的地方。"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她拾起一株稻穗。"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_snow_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 8.0, "ystrength": 6.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_frmrwkhrd"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbootwalk"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1242_1#8$1", "duration": 1.5, "bstart": 0.15, "bend": 0.5}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 8.0, "ystrength": 6.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_frmrwkhrd"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "模糊的身影揮舞著鋤頭，將一粒粒種子埋進地裡。"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_140#2", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您回來了？！太好了，大家都在等您呢！", "name": "忙碌的農民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_140#2"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您這次走了好久，路上還順利嗎？有沒有找到想找的莊稼？", "name": "忙碌的農民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_140#2"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1242_1#8$1", "bstart": 0.15, "bend": 0.5}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "action": "shake", "power": 6.0, "times": 35.0, "duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_140#2"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老師……您還好嗎？您看起來有點……", "name": "忙碌的農民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_140#2"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "MusicVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_140#1"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這……這是什麼？！", "name": "忙碌的農民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_140#1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "救命——救命！", "name": "忙碌的農民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_140#1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "47_g7_fieldhouse", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "MusicVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1240_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1240_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小禾？你怎麼還在這？", "name": "老鄉長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1240_1#6$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我查到了……", "name": "禾生"}, "figure_art": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#9$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "污染……不是跟著洪水過來的，污染源應該在地下才對。", "name": "禾生"}, "figure_art": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#9$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在集合天師府的人手，把握時間開始研究應該還來得及！", "name": "禾生"}, "figure_art": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#5$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1240_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別研究了。", "name": "老鄉長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1240_1#3$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1240_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "已經決定了，要放棄這些地了……", "name": "老鄉長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1240_1#2$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不會耽誤太多時間的！可能只要兩三天，我就能鎖定污染來源，肯定會有解決辦法的！", "name": "禾生"}, "figure_art": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大荒城每一厘田地都來之不易，我們都還沒有努力過，怎麼能說放棄就放棄了——", "name": "禾生"}, "figure_art": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#7$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1240_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是幾片地塊，是整座大荒城。", "name": "老鄉長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1240_1#1$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼……？", "name": "禾生"}, "figure_art": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#7$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1240_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明天之前，所有人都要搬到核心城上去，跟著核心城向東遷移，其他田地就丟在這裡。", "name": "老鄉長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1240_1#1$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其他天師都在著手組織大家搬家的事，這才是現在最要緊的事……你也去幫忙吧。", "name": "老鄉長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1240_1#1$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是……誰的主意？", "name": "禾生"}, "figure_art": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1240_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能下令讓一城搬遷的，你覺得呢？", "name": "老鄉長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1240_1#3$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼……", "name": "禾生"}, "figure_art": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些試驗田，還有這些才種下去的作物……", "name": "禾生"}, "figure_art": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今年已經是荒年，如果再放棄這些莊稼，會有多少人餓肚子。", "name": "禾生"}, "figure_art": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……就像回到以前的時候。", "name": "禾生"}, "figure_art": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1240_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們盡力了。", "name": "老鄉長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1240_1#4$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "儘早將人力撤走，儘早準備災後應對措施。你是天師府的天師，別在這種時候分不清——", "name": "老鄉長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1240_1#4$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "神話是真的……？", "name": "禾生"}, "figure_art": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1240_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說什麼傻話……", "name": "老鄉長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1240_1#6$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "河北岸的凍土，藏著什麼東西？就是它們污染了土地，對不對？", "name": "禾生"}, "figure_art": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1240_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就當是一場天災。", "name": "老鄉長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1240_1#7$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多少年來，我們保護不了的東西還少嗎……", "name": "老鄉長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1240_1#7$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大家不會走的。", "name": "禾生"}, "figure_art": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#5$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是我們的土地，不弄明白這裡到底發生了什麼，大家都不會走的。", "name": "禾生"}, "figure_art": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#5$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "神農能把這些敵人擋在家園外面，我們也能。", "name": "禾生"}, "figure_art": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#5$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1240_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "老鄉長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1240_1#2$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "47_g13_pollutedfield", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "47_g7_fieldhouse", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是幻覺嗎？"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "眼前廣闊的田地瞬間變得荒蕪。"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不是田地荒蕪，而是這一方天地都被另一片空間侵噬，這已不是人們熟悉的土地。"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那邊是怎麼回事？！", "name": "禾生"}, "figure_art": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#7$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1240_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來不及了……", "name": "老鄉長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1240_1#8$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_snow_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_magic_5"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_kneelsnow_s", "delay": 0.2}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$monastery_sad_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_140#1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黍姑娘，剛才那到底是什麼東西……", "name": "受驚的農民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_140#1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老師她……生病了嗎？她為什麼會變成這副模樣？", "name": "受驚的農民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_140#1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#16$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#16$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "把她，安葬了吧……", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#3$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbootwalk"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一具瘦削的身軀倒在冷硬的土地上，單薄的衣衫口袋裡，裝著一小袋種子。"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_140#1"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是她帶回來的種子？她找到傳說中的種子了嗎？", "name": "受驚的農民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_140#1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這兩年收成實在不好，有了這袋種子，說不定還有希望……", "name": "受驚的農民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_140#1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_140#2"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們把它帶回去……", "name": "受驚的農民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_140#2"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "47_g6_civilengineermasteroffice", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ponder_intro", "key": "$ponder_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#3$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "邪魔的污染，為什麼在地下？", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#3$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天機閣不是在外邊守著？那些污染物是怎麼繞過老傢伙跑進來的？", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#3$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "根據現在的觀測結果推算，這裡的污染物早在還沒有天機閣的時候就已經存在了。", "name": "天機閣天師"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這片土地的地下，已經被高度侵染了。", "name": "天機閣天師"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但這麼多年來邪魔影響都沒有擴散，是因為她在這裡？", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#3$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可為什麼現在這個時候……她難道……", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#3$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "災難來源，天機閣大抵已有判斷。但當務之急是應對眼下危機。", "name": "天機閣天師"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這次邪魔災害的影響前所未有，情況在天機閣所有預案之外。", "name": "天機閣天師"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們天機閣的天師竟然主動找我……現在還有什麼辦法？", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#8$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "北岸天機閣全線後撤，同時將對邪魔的防線向南後撤五十公里。", "name": "天機閣天師"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "丟棄一切地塊，只撤離核心城，之後需要你協助啟動核心城的部分防禦功能，以核心城為屏障重新設立防線。", "name": "天機閣天師"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個方案，聽起來沒有討論犧牲人數對吧？", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#8$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "邪魔穢物不比一般的災害，務必當斷則斷。", "name": "天機閣天師"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可沒看過大炎做這麼消極的判斷，這是誰的命令？", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#3$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……是你們的上頭，那個見首不見尾的老天師的意思？", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#3$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽命行事即可，勿要多問。", "name": "天機閣天師"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "夕"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#1$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在看什麼？", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#8$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……她為什麼要這麼做？", "name": "夕"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#9$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她大概是真的捨不得這裡吧……", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#6$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果早在那個時候，邪魔就已經污染到這片土地的下面……這麼多年，全靠她在壓制著。", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#6$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一千年……意識被邪魔啃噬了整整一千年，會是什麼感覺……", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#6$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個姐姐……真是……", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#6$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在沒有別的辦法了？", "name": "夕"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#9$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們也無能為力，你不能用一張畫把這裡的人全都帶走，我也沒辦法憑空造一座可以運走所有人的城。", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#3$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那，她呢？", "name": "夕"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#9$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼意思……", "name": "年"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2014_nian_1#8$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她難道會不知道，遲早有這麼一天嗎？", "name": "夕"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#9$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她現在……在哪裡？", "name": "夕"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_2015_dusk_1#2$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "47_g2_desertedcityfield_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1240_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1240_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "老鄉長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1240_1#3$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_wind", "channel": "2"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_drtywndblw", "delay": 1.0}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哭聲。"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哭聲從很遠的地方傳來，是嬰兒啼哭，老人啜泣幽咽，田裡的莊稼也在悲鳴。"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "彷彿是四十年前的一幕。"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那也是一個荒年。"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "35_mini01_villagevacancy", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$m_sys_bitw_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "你就是黍？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#2$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#18$1"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是……從司歲台來的人？", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#18$1"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "你受命在大荒城耕種，近年天災頻傳，已經連年歉收。你作為代理人明明有能力救活這些莊稼，但卻選擇袖手旁觀？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#4$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的能力，人們沒辦法復現。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我救了這一次，之後人們便只會想著這樣的“神蹟”如何才能再發生。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#15$1"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可我做不到每一次都能救下所有……總有一天，我會消失不見的。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#15$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到那時，我現在用的力量，只會變成害人的“惡因”。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#15$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.4, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "你難道無可奈何？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.4, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我能做的的確不多……只是把過去的經驗記下來，告訴後來的人。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "災年過去，總會有豐年，人們總得靠自己來扛過這一切。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#1$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.4, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "可我該怎麼相信，你留在這裡，是在做於炎國、於百姓有益的事？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.4, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#13$1"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#13$1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#14$1"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你會在這裡留多久？", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#14$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.4, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "……直到明年這個時候。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.4, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_2025_shu_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等今年收穫的時候，你會看到的。", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#9$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，你下過地嗎？", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#9$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在正是插秧的時候，大家都忙得很，能不能請你來幫個忙？", "name": "黍"}, "figure_art": "avg_2025_shu_1#9$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我依稀記得，那一年的莊稼，長得特別好。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "打下來的稻穀堆成了小山，職農們說，接下來幾年再遇上天災都不用害怕。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你笑了？", "name": "黍"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "……我很開心。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "給司歲台的記錄上，還準備打我的小報告嗎？", "name": "黍"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "你會一直留在這嗎？留在這幫我們……", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "有你在，大家就可以安心了。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "黍"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我曾經有一個朋友，和你很像。", "name": "黍"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "47_g11_shuresearchoffice", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.7, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "……", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "現在，我們實在沒有辦法。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "一次就好……我只懇求你這一次。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "能不能請你，救一次這裡的人？", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "你答應過我，會一直留在這裡……", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_glassdooropen"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1240_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黍……", "name": "老鄉長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1240_1#1$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "房間是空的。"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "桌上還留有一碗溫熱的湯。"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1240_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你……原來早就……", "name": "老鄉長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1240_1#8$1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_thunders_amb"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "下雨了。"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "47_g2_desertedcityfield_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1250_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "下雨了？", "name": "田邊的職農"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1250_1#1$1"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_slmddrprn"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_rainheavy_loop", "loop": "true", "channel": "a", "delay": 3.0}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "農人抬起頭，看到一縷輕薄的雲層遮住了天邊的新月，不一會，幾滴清涼的雨水便落了下來。"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1250_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是誰……？", "name": "田邊的職農"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1250_1#1$1"}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "image", "attributes": {"image": "47_i14_1", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.05, "yScale": 1.05}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.05, "yScaleFrom": 1.05, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 30.0}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遠處，有一人向農田深處走去。"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她在荒蕪的田地上走過，足跡踏過的地方，生出些許綠意。"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“喂，你要上哪去？”"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她沒有應答，只是向前走去。"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_thunders_amb"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "image", "attributes": {"image": "47_i14_2", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她越走越遠，身影在一聲夏雷中消散。"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不同於幾日前的那場暴雨，此時的雨水竟是那樣細密、柔和。"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雨水落下，土地的皸裂盡數褪去。"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個被禁錮了千年的遊魂在此時消散。"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萬物生長。"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "47_g2_desertedcityfield_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_rain", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 399, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老師？", "name": "禾生"}, "figure_art": "avg_4119_wanqin_1#8$1"}, {"id": 402, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 403, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 405, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 407, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_landscape", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4121_zuole_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1236_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "n